  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/883fcaf480321b598062fde7b57af829.avif?t=1711612239\" width=600 height=118 /></span><br><strong><i>Deep in the caves, surrounded by unknown monsters...</i></strong> Voxel Miner: Dwellers of the Deep, is a single player game where you mine resources to upgrade different skills, abilities, and fight the creatures you come across along the way! Strategize your upgrades, fight monsters, or just sit back and enjoy the satisfying mechanics. The choice is yours...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/e4d5aa35dabec6b85a26718f98accd4d.webp?t=1711612239\" width=600 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Procedural map generation, no two worlds are the same!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Endless gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Variety of unique upgrades.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Satisfying gameplay mechanics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Customizable player styles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Stylized art style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Beautiful soundtrack.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Amazing sound design.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Customizable settings.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Detailed stats.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Leaderboards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Achievements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Custom world generation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Custom texture manager.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Controller support.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/86b0a7fb5a1f32da4374b7dff7f8b86e.webp?t=1711612239\" width=600 height=62 /></span><br>Voxel Miner: Dwellers of the Deep immerses players in a gripping tale of scientific ambition and peril. A team of brilliant scientists creates ACEROS (who you play as), an advanced autonomous robot, to combat the relentless virus called the \"Subterrovirus\" that transforms humans into stone. As ACEROS explores the infected depths, it gets infected by the virus, and evolves into a sentient entity, turning on its creators after learning they are trying to make its purpose obsolete.<br><br>Caught in a dilemma, the scientists realize they depend on ACEROS to understand the virus, even if ACEROS poses a threat. The delicate balance between human-AI collaboration and potential destruction unfolds. Through sacrifices and ethical dilemmas, the fate of humanity hangs in the balance as the secrets of the Subterrovirus are uncovered.<br><br>Voxel Miner: Dwellers of the Deep contains a thrilling narrative that explores the risks and rewards of seeking knowledge in the face of an unstoppable threat. <strong>Prepare to learn about a riveting journey through scientific discovery, human-AI dynamics, and the echoes of a transforming world.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/11a9f572e9a607d23714de20baf256d2.webp?t=1711612239\" width=600 height=12 /></span><br><br><i>- This game is a passion project of mine, with close to two years in development I'm proud to release this game.  I tried making this as accessible as possible to anyone, and the price shows that.  This game isn't $5 because it doesn't merit a higher price, it is $5 because I want people to experience this game I have put thousands of hours into developing.  Every single purchase is seen by me, and greatly appreciated, any feedback, suggestions, or questions sent in our discord are responded to quickly by myself.  Thank you for considering and/or getting this game and supporting my dream! -</i><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/11a9f572e9a607d23714de20baf256d2.webp?t=1711612239\" width=600 height=12 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/883fcaf480321b598062fde7b57af829.avif?t=1711612239\" width=600 height=118 /></span><br><strong><i>Deep in the caves, surrounded by unknown monsters...</i></strong> Voxel Miner: Dwellers of the Deep, is a single player game where you mine resources to upgrade different skills, abilities, and fight the creatures you come across along the way! Strategize your upgrades, fight monsters, or just sit back and enjoy the satisfying mechanics. The choice is yours...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/e4d5aa35dabec6b85a26718f98accd4d.webp?t=1711612239\" width=600 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Procedural map generation, no two worlds are the same!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Endless gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Variety of unique upgrades.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extras/b0619d90ab2693eaa51c7a8af59bb891.webp?t=1711612239\" width=5 height=8 /></span>  Satisfying gameplay mechanics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113220/extra